Package movieDBquiz

This package contains the components to make a movie quiz for the most recently playing 20 movies.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DbManager
    Class that manages information obtained from the TMDB.
    Main
    Driver utility class for running the movie quiz.
    MatchingQuestion
    Class that creates matching questions for a movie trivia quiz using the TMDB API.
    Quiz
    Driver for the movie quiz.
    QuizDemo
    Creates a GUI for the movie quiz and allows for user interaction.
    Randomize
    This class is used to randomize questions and answers for the movie quiz.
    TestMatchingQuestion
    Tests all methods in the MatchingQuestion Class.

Package movieDBquiz Description

This package contains the components to make a movie quiz for the most recently playing 20 movies.
